{"tid":1042063,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"西口西面去西藏 （龜速打字撚）","createTime":"2019-03-01T09:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T12:35:57.000Z","uid":188673,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"54142f2d668665b58fbc89bed79d3be531731edd","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一次打遊記！</span><br />\n本來想一路去一路打<br />\n但發現真係太懶太攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拖到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係度屎忽痕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好！費話少講<br />\n開始！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先打一啲前期<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">準備功夫</span>先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地就計劃5月尾去 <br />\n4月尾先開始話想去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就上網搵左人拼車 計劃大約去幾日同幾號去<br />\n通常10-14日 計埋適應下高反<br />\n先再買機票同車飛<br />\n但後尾先知去到再拼車都得~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n5月頭就拿拿林買機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機票火車方面:<br />\n<br />\n去程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHk去西寧 下晝機到西寧已經零晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中途停北京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    💰3700左右 兩個<br />\n西寧訓一晚 <br />\n<br />\n再坐火車去拉薩 💰1300左右 兩個 <br />\n(火車係6個人果隻，分上中下)無得揀位嫁<br />\n我同旅伴就一上一下<br />\n好在唔係訓中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎飛先知訓邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉薩返Hk <br />\n中途停四川<br />\n第二日先返    💰HK4300左右 兩個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解唔直航去西藏呢？</span><br />\n一泥係想適應下<br />\n二泥係想坐下火車🚞 係好好嘅體驗<br />\n你會見到晒一年四季咁～加上你又可以落車打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我個人認為 <br />\n西寧去西藏21個鐘真係夠晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事關第二日架車開始污衊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(係個厠所已經浮屎 水喉都塞埋)<br />\n而家諗反起，好彩無係廣州上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無諗過頂唔順要即刻返泥？<br />\n當然會有！但都要買定回程機票<br />\n我之前上網做過reseach發現都好多人無買回程 <br />\n結果係無！機！位！<br />\n一係就好貴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以自己衡量啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拼車方面：<br />\n一開始本身諗住搵唔到/唉坐得舒服啲兩個人一架算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n好好彩見到2個女仔同我地差唔多日子去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重要係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人</span></strong><br />\n咁岩仲係差唔多年紀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強烈建議！</span><br />\n搵反香港人🇭🇰唔係話岐視乜乜乜<br />\n係你成個旅程10幾日基本上都一齊坐車一齊食一齊玩<br />\n如果搵反台灣人內地人 大家口味生活方式都唔同<br />\n加上言語不通 好易有拗撬<br />\n(當然你想識朋友另計啦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係搵左好多個網 <br />\n最後就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">背包客棧</span> 度同佢地拼<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去西藏都有分唔同路線 我自己就無乜所謂嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我去之前基本上係對西藏零認識<br />\n純粹sem break去旅行<br />\n咁叫旅伴搵下佢有咩地方係想去同<span style=\"color: violet;\">MUST</span>要去嘅<br />\n<br />\n係你兩手空空同我一樣 完全一頭霧水嘅時候！<br />\n基本上你係唔洗點plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPlan ge只係點去西藏<br />\n留幾多日係拉薩？ 同埋點撘過去呢？<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係我地拼車嘅行程：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD1：拉薩-<span style=\"color: red;\">羊湖</span>--卡若拉冰川--江孜--宗山城堡--日喀則(宿)<br />\nD2：日喀則--扎什倫布寺--新定日--絨布寺--珠峰大本營（宿）<br />\nD3：<span style=\"color: red;\">珠峰大本營</span>--老定日（崗噶）--希夏邦馬保護區--佩枯錯--薩嘎(宿)<br />\nD4：薩嘎--巴嘎--基烏寺--拉昂錯--瑪旁雍錯--神山岡仁波齊--塔欽(宿)<br />\nD5：塔欽--門士--巴爾兵站--扎達--古格--札達（宿）<br />\nD6：札達--古格王朝--扎達土林--仲巴（宿）<br />\nD7：仲巴--拉孜（宿）<br />\nD8：拉孜--日喀則--尼木草原--那根拉山口--納木錯（宿）<br />\nD9：<span style=\"color: red;\">納木錯</span>--念青唐古拉山--羊八井--拉薩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次去西藏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">準備</span>：<br />\n<br />\n藥: <br />\ndiamox 食完會勁急尿 腳痺👈🏿我自己覺得無乜特別用處 都係頭兩日坐火車有食 之後去高山已經無食(費事急尿😳）我朋友就上高山都有食 但佢都有高山反應 所以我自己就覺得隻藥未必有用 買定有備無患~<br />\n不過都有少少貴 買完食左一排都無<br />\n<br />\n紅景天 (兩星期前要食）(人食我食系列)<br />\n<br />\n感冒藥 好多好多（平時有食開見效快果種）<br />\n<br />\n頭痛藥 <br />\n<br />\n止嘔止瀉藥 (啲野食相對比較油)怕食唔慣<br />\n<br />\n暈車浪啲藥？！(長時間坐車，你本身易暈就帶啦)<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">防曬！</span> 1-2枝 唔好以為男仔唔洗帶<br />\n係會曬傷 因為太接近太陽 加上紫外線好高<br />\n你去到雖然唔覺 但反到泥就知味道<br />\n起碼都要茶面  <br />\n<br />\n保濕 dry到爆 我就帶蘆薈噴霧 懶得茶 但都係帶cream會好啲<br />\n<br />\nMasksssssss去幾多日就帶幾多塊 最好 晚晚敷 <br />\n<br />\n喉糖  <br />\n(呢樣我又覺得唔洗太多)就係聽左好多人講帶多啲，喉糖太甜 食完你又想狂飲水 但又無厠所仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(話就話周圍都係厠所姐)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打住前期先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下有無人想繼續睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有問題都可以留底嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afeed99c35cff308fa147e90160de3152ada6b14","tid":1042063,"uid":49992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"4月頭會出發 硬臥係咪冇差電位？？"},{"pid":"7ea71b4e1a9c9e30fdf3b19f510ef82cc8fd4088","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afeed99c35cff308fa147e90160de3152ada6b14","tid":1042063,"uid":49992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"4月頭會出發 硬臥係咪冇差電位？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"我上次硬卧就係房外走廊啲枱底 但最好係帶定後備電"},{"pid":"1bab7476072326bf034cb379f2394ba6de2ca2cb","tid":1042063,"uid":185296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08442ab9293b6f7d7a4cee83f8b45e4bb1a93829","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bab7476072326bf034cb379f2394ba6de2ca2cb","tid":1042063,"uid":185296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:16:22.000Z","msg":"滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為無人睇"},{"pid":"008d9672df63ff9ebcae8e38785ef0a954e82109","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"衫:<br />\n     <br />\n     風褸 風褸褲 防風防水 <br />\n     雨絨 uniquo超薄 /薄得泥保暖<br />\n     Heattech!!! 4-5件 衫 褲<br />\n     衛衣 帶多兩件 （<br />\n     最好有件有毛係入面 有件係無毛）<br />\n     短衫一兩件 （沙漠熱到傻）<br />\n     超厚嘅褲 入面有毛(淘寶都得 幾十蚊)1條<br />\n     帶啲舒適嘅褲 （坐多過行）<br />\n     一定一定要帶<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">厚襪</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">厚襪</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">厚襪</span>！ ！ ！我就係無帶！腳趾凍   到傻 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n零食:  <br />\n<br />\n      杯麵2個啦(係費事口痕/上火車食)<br />\n      朱古力多小小 （我中意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n    （食完多小小能量+保暖）（當你食唔落野就有用啦）<br />\n      零食乾糧 （樓主太中意食零食mode)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(帶多小小上車食下 有時會因為趕行程無野食嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然當地都有零食買)<br />\n      鹹濕食品(柑桔🍊果類)呢個好重要！解渴得泥又唔會成日急尿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上網卡方面:<br />\n<br />\n大眾幾好用 上得幾快<br />\n左邊就慢小小 但都上到<br />\n我fd就用people好多人介紹果張 佢係全程要借我上網嘅<br />\n但唔好expect上得好快果種 係上到 但要啲時間先load到ig<br />\n畢竟去旅行嘛 當上網報下平安算<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/132009_a61d18f3dbf1510c214b3309ccec3812.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F132009_a61d18f3dbf1510c214b3309ccec3812.png&h=ad8dcfc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df61477d9b5bd69b207059c76141987a11bea4c5","tid":1042063,"uid":49992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"4月頭出發有咩注意"},{"pid":"02cd49e631907dc7f797ae174a7f2fb249aa2666","tid":1042063,"uid":7770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384ca8cfbe6c35bf591ec064f27545f75ac2ed31","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df61477d9b5bd69b207059c76141987a11bea4c5","tid":1042063,"uid":49992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"4月頭出發有咩注意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:51:31.000Z","msg":"天氣方面有機會凍過我小小<br />\n帶多一兩件厚衫!<br />\n同埋有機會去珠峰落大雪<br />\n<br />\n你係book車？"},{"pid":"e117e051cf64d465c703832f7dd86f399864a025","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:53:23.000Z","msg":"訂<span style=\"color: red;\">酒店</span>小小小TIPsssss:<br />\n<br />\n基本上你淨係要諗去程未join團之前租邊間同埋回程返拉薩住邊<br />\n<br />\nJoin團係完全唔洗諗！<br />\n因為佢司機雖然俾個行程你 <br />\n但有機會因應天氣有唔同 可能調前後次序<br />\n<br />\n到時再book都得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我會打返我到果度有咩酒店住過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">推薦/覺得唔好住</span>嘅地方俾大家"},{"pid":"009401682f3b01edfccc54f9e6cc639502dcbf87","tid":1042063,"uid":49992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"384ca8cfbe6c35bf591ec064f27545f75ac2ed31","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df61477d9b5bd69b207059c76141987a11bea4c5","tid":1042063,"uid":49992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"4月頭出發有咩注意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:51:31.000Z","msg":"天氣方面有機會凍過我小小<br />\n帶多一兩件厚衫!<br />\n同埋有機會去珠峰落大雪<br />\n<br />\n你係book車？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:10:12.000Z","msg":"去到先揾 local tour"},{"pid":"54236ce851811ce804c8c2fc1b5316d21c862b8d","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:13:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Day 1</span>:<br />\n<br />\n坐左成日飛機去西寧<br />\n1535-1910（我就航班延誤 2030先到佢話壞冷氣）<br />\nHk airline &mdash;&mdash;去北京再轉飛西寧<br />\n去北京無delay就3hr35mins<br />\n通常delay 2hrs <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/140934_36016334e9c19bb34f8bcc47b0392640.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F140934_36016334e9c19bb34f8bcc47b0392640.png&h=bbad508d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機餐一如既往地難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/140935_b774d7c57ce74aba62708380aad04a74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F140935_b774d7c57ce74aba62708380aad04a74.png&h=4acc554e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落機拎完行李就行去另一個客運大樓轉飛西寧<br />\n第一次去北京 。。。個機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都幾大<br />\n<br />\n而且好麻煩地要安檢🛂<br />\nHea得泥又慢吞吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/140938_d914295bc1bb43a10e85e57301c2b7a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F140938_d914295bc1bb43a10e85e57301c2b7a6.png&h=ecf534ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/140941_a06ae0cfaccfdb6441b4e40c8389fd40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F140941_a06ae0cfaccfdb6441b4e40c8389fd40.png&h=cc2896c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/140942_334e40b1bfee8b4e364d79241431ed19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F140942_334e40b1bfee8b4e364d79241431ed19.png&h=b1eab9da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff35d5d2c1968ec13e7f6643f022afac813390ff","tid":1042063,"uid":7275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f159e84d6331fc779e42b70bcc8c8298b3797b15","tid":1042063,"uid":32464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想去"},{"pid":"11da8d28be946c29228cd4e9a5e49a7b34ae2ad4","tid":1042063,"uid":185296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T07:11:27.000Z","msg":"好想去 但怕自己身體handle唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c09f8607e9f51789412672803eb6e18b7bacd8","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f159e84d6331fc779e42b70bcc8c8298b3797b15","tid":1042063,"uid":32464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"想去就去馬啦！"},{"pid":"fd536412ec16c95ec789b71c29c156c54dac9f1c","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11da8d28be946c29228cd4e9a5e49a7b34ae2ad4","tid":1042063,"uid":185296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T07:11:27.000Z","msg":"好想去 但怕自己身體handle唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"唔洗怕喎！<br />\n而家咁多藥 去到唔掂即反泥都得啦"},{"pid":"92e4857535829bac99adce43966ebc08ca5fea57","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"落機拎完行李就行去另一個客運大樓轉飛西寧<br />\n都仲有小小時間<br />\n可以食反小小野先<br />\n<br />\n去到已經無乜餐廳開<br />\n求其搵反間醫下肚仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拌麵就真係唔係幾得囉！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/165323_bbcebccdaaaf05cac85b0aeefe12d123.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F165323_bbcebccdaaaf05cac85b0aeefe12d123.png&h=e2070cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雲吞麵就幾好食 不過唔夠熱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/165325_ab19ee85533ce08e1f0ab2566ca81849.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F165325_ab19ee85533ce08e1f0ab2566ca81849.png&h=6ba73434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上機啦！<br />\n咁上機就同左個姨姨吹下水 佢就介紹我地6月去西寧睇花海話真係好靚 <br />\n<br />\n順帶講一講<br />\n呢個機場熱到飛起囉。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/165326_e3f544ea4e97d5d8da0199afad4290cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F165326_e3f544ea4e97d5d8da0199afad4290cd.png&h=effac6aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手震版西寧上空<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/165328_63e91fbbd86a8b1c628e57e05bb95344.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F165328_63e91fbbd86a8b1c628e57e05bb95344.png&h=59adca69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/165329_8f1ca5aa1974ba015dd431e56af3f870.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F165329_8f1ca5aa1974ba015dd431e56af3f870.png&h=7cc3d5ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得一兩條行李輸送帶<br />\n同沖繩機場個大細差唔多🤔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/165331_453e5749f117b44b984aa57c9e51276f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F165331_453e5749f117b44b984aa57c9e51276f.png&h=2c00a72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出機場已經好夜 係咩車都無咁濟<br />\n一係等聽朝巴士一係行一係坐的士<br />\n<br />\n咁你都係焗住撘的士。。。<br />\n仲要得一兩架 <br />\n咁自然就會開天價 <span style=\"color: red;\">400蚊</span>喎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好過去搶！</span><br />\n<br />\n咁最後講價150人仔2個人去 但只係半個鐘路程<br />\n<br />\n世界上所有的士被人叫<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">的士狗</span></strong>係唔會無原因 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">小插曲</span> <br />\n<br />\n講完價 又話即走啦 <br />\n佢叫我地上車 <br />\n咁我地好自然上車梗係以為佢開車 <br />\n點知佢係度等喎？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲接多2條友 大佬呀 咁你即咩走<br />\n係大陸我就覺得盡量唔同人地一架車<br />\n感覺<strong>好危險</strong> 人生路不熟<br />\n<br />\n佢架的士又舊舊地 點知會唔會打劫嫁<br />\n仲有會感覺到佢地梗係有種<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">賊眉賊眼</span>feel"},{"pid":"97f196e2b69d0423c49de758d2ff606537adf687","tid":1042063,"uid":49992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:25:37.000Z","msg":"op加油，等你出相"},{"pid":"7fe24f3c88da5c15b91e8eeddfa5a63d6c60e75a","tid":1042063,"uid":85591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"劉明，囡囡摩牙"},{"pid":"1c1f2c0b0a0153d714346a1cc1604b5be4c50fb4","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"我就訂左呢間300幾蚊<br />\n貪佢近車站 係火車隔離<br />\n第二日下晝先上火車<br />\n可以行下再反泥拎行李<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/190003_c16167b67809bb59e2105d42d042ec34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F190003_c16167b67809bb59e2105d42d042ec34.png&h=d04686a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 2: <br />\n<br />\n酒店包兩個人早餐！<br />\n無期望過係好食<br />\nUm 但味道真係 唔係幾好<br />\n個奶淡過水<br />\n<br />\n有得加早餐可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔使加</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/190132_836c76286634b7af9d9a22c318dd0302.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F190132_836c76286634b7af9d9a22c318dd0302.png&h=44d893fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以都係決定喺商場行個圈<br />\n求其搵間野醫下肚仔先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/190642_8f615399a9028dc65b8f92dfd398d8ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F190642_8f615399a9028dc65b8f92dfd398d8ca.png&h=170b4f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/190644_016fe69dd51cc9637764da459cba1492.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F190644_016fe69dd51cc9637764da459cba1492.png&h=d505f97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日頭嘅西寧站<br />\n酒店一行出黎就見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勁方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/190646_16e27c948fb3692db4edd77f213a5168.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F190646_16e27c948fb3692db4edd77f213a5168.png&h=0cd30849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口痕買左野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/190647_bb97e9f46d6fbe83cd1181aba122b649.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F190647_bb97e9f46d6fbe83cd1181aba122b649.png&h=627c573d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53ee7f3938ddfcbfada18dd01d4f2d078a41b66b","tid":1042063,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"西藏好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去過兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1594223b389b386a03a2d4de5ea7acb5c9ba30","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53ee7f3938ddfcbfada18dd01d4f2d078a41b66b","tid":1042063,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"西藏好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去過兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"唔同線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de43dbccacfc7074962db37501b1ba3d4e77a1d","tid":1042063,"uid":67976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"LM 仲喺西藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51481dbf4bdbd2786cf5b4cc9ab43006cc4ba893","tid":1042063,"uid":182419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:20:56.000Z","msg":"Lm參考 同班frd七月去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1540980fa51ca672d4f55f08ea46de195233c6ca","tid":1042063,"uid":52004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"留名下年去"},{"pid":"4d9398d99aed456e06bff5e579e5d66b45d60be1","tid":1042063,"uid":126590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"佢d站停一停就走，都係一樣樣，所以打卡的話係影下站名就冇其他<br />\n<br />\n回程時搭過，同埋台灣人唔去得西藏架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1f38072f9f676394fbedbf2b6eac5a9af70d65","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"Day 2朝早:<br />\n<br />\n原本冇諗過第2日會早起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起左就搵個寺行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上諗住上火車大把時間訓😈<br />\n<br />\n我哋酒店出發去 係搭咗的士🚕<br />\n大約都係幾十蚊<br />\n費事煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />速去速回<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n青海省西寧市金塔路56號（海拔：2696米）<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係撘尔寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地話叫小布達拉宮<br />\n佢有分學生門票同埋成人門票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">樓主實測</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係唔關香港學生事！</span><br />\n之後再俾返<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正價</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋佢呢度都有得俾錢導遊帶你行反轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樓主呢～<br />\n普通話就唔係咁得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上佢都有牌俾你睇下小小歷史野<br />\n但有興趣可以自己再加錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5UWfmO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5UWfmO.png&h=b6fc6f36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bf5qS8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbf5qS8v.png&h=f555f970&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3CT11R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3CT11R.png&h=f04b73a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寺入面都有好多地方係唔俾影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我覺得呢間唔算捉得好嚴<br />\n好多唔俾影相嘅位都好多人影緊相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQnQjOy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQnQjOy.png&h=4f19ac0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xN8zMtz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxN8zMtz.png&h=434d55b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NqQBZOB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqQBZOB.png&h=283c123c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSVVvVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSVVvVh.png&h=18983d59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnL2VmY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnL2VmY.png&h=69bebf65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFxHVmZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFxHVmZ.png&h=d126d0d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W6c8QVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW6c8QVk.png&h=da0392af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面都有大多西藏寺一樣都係宮殿式建築<br />\n而呢度最出名嘅係酥油花、壁畫同堆繡<br />\n不過我對歷史野係零知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋入面有個位好多人都係度跪拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係第一次親眼見到人哋跪拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n轉經筒是唔可以逆時針轉嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4a2bbd6c1312434afbf41eb752eca6fdd4653b","tid":1042063,"uid":188673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d9398d99aed456e06bff5e579e5d66b45d60be1","tid":1042063,"uid":126590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"佢d站停一停就走，都係一樣樣，所以打卡的話係影下站名就冇其他<br />\n<br />\n回程時搭過，同埋台灣人唔去得西藏架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"佢地去得 但係一定要跟團咋嘛🤔<br />\n我會落去買零食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有啲站落去睇日落🌄"},{"pid":"b3b335feab35811aebf8d127dd6f702ae336f188","tid":1042063,"uid":241537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"